02:27.230 --> 02:29.606
<i>STEVE: ...everybody's</i>
<i>favorite game show</i>

02:29.607 --> 02:32.693
<i>with lots of fun and fabulous prizes.</i>

02:32.694 --> 02:35.571
<i>And the best prize of all,</i>

02:35.738 --> 02:38.949
<i>...the sumptuous, the sultry,</i>
<i>the scintillating, Susan Starr!</i>

02:39.284 --> 02:40.993
[ Audience clapping ]

02:42.287 --> 02:44.955
<i>MAN: Come on, bitch.</i>
<i>Let's play the game.</i>

02:46.082 --> 02:46.957
[ Doll squeaks ]

02:47.333 --> 02:49.501
<i>Who is going to play the game today?</i>

02:49.502 --> 02:50.169
<i>ANNOUNCER: Yes, Steve,</i>

02:50.170 --> 02:53.755
<i>our first contestants are</i>
<i>Pat Brown and Ron Reilly.</i>

02:54.048 --> 02:56.008
<i>-STEVE: Welcome, contestants.</i>
<i>-PAT: Thank you, Steve.</i>

02:56.217 --> 02:57.301
<i>RON: Hi, Steve.</i>

02:57.302 --> 02:59.344
<i>STEVE: John, tell us what's in store</i>
<i>for our players today.</i>

02:59.512 --> 03:02.514
<i>ANNOUNCER: Steve,</i>
<i>today our grand prize is...</i>

03:02.515 --> 03:04.683
<i>two luxurious weeks in...</i>

03:04.851 --> 03:06.643
- [ Doll squeaks ]
<i>-ANNOUNCER: ...Hawaii!</i>

03:06.644 --> 03:07.644
<i>ANNOUNCER: That's right!</i>

03:07.645 --> 03:12.941
