PRISONER: There is no ''R''.

04:02.242 --> 04:04.076
<i>- [ Buzzer ]</i>
<i>- STEVE: Oh, I'm sorry, Ron.</i>

04:04.077 --> 04:05.410
<i>STEVE: There is no ''R''.</i>

04:05.912 --> 04:07.663
Would you like to finish
your last meal, sir?

04:07.664 --> 04:10.207
<i>STEVE: What was the occupation</i>
<i>of Jack the Ripper's five victims?</i>

