04:24.097 --> 04:25.430
<i>STEVE: Yes, there is.</i>

04:25.431 --> 04:27.099
[ Continued clapping ]

04:27.558 --> 04:29.351
Do you know what I'd like?

04:29.811 --> 04:31.770
I'd like one of these motherfuckers...

04:32.522 --> 04:34.064
