04:35.525 --> 04:37.276
[ Laughs ]

04:38.486 --> 04:40.696
[ Prisoner laughing ]

04:45.702 --> 04:48.996
<i>STEVE: Okay, then, your chance</i>
<i>to get lucky and win...</i>

04:56.379 --> 04:59.840
<i>...clouds in the sky.</i>
<i>Now, look up and what letters --</i>

05:02.051 --> 05:05.012
- [ Buzzer ]
<i>-ALL: Aww!</i>

05:05.680 --> 05:07.681
<i>STEVE: Okay, it's time</i>
<i>for our bonus question.</i>

05:07.682 --> 05:09.599
<i>What's our bonus prize?</i>

05:13.021 --> 05:14.563
<i>ANNOUNCER: If you'd like to be</i>
<i>a contestant</i>

05:14.564 --> 05:15.981
<i>or a member of our studio audience,</i>

