<i>stamped postcard</i>

05:18.192 --> 05:23.030
<i>to Wheelers and Dealers, Box 12,</i>
<i>Hollywood, California, 90038.</i>

05:23.031 --> 05:26.074
<i>And now, Steve, here are</i>
<i>our next two contestants,</i>

05:26.284 --> 05:29.369
<i>Sylvia Chance and Paul Dean.</i>

05:30.955 --> 05:35.334
<i>-PAUL: I'm a marketing analyst from --</i>
<i>-Hiya, Steve! Good to be here.</i>

05:35.335 --> 05:38.378
<i>I'm a poodle groomer</i>
<i>from Hackensack, New Jersey.</i>

05:38.379 --> 05:40.589
