<i>our fabulous prize package</i>

05:40.757 --> 05:43.091
<i>includes a genuine leather,</i>
<i>swivel, rocker recliner,</i>

05:43.092 --> 05:45.177
<i>featuring adjustable</i>
<i>head and foot positions,</i>

05:45.178 --> 05:49.890
<i>added ruffle velour arms, and magic</i>
<i>massage with computer memory,</i>

05:50.183 --> 05:52.267
<i>made from handcrafted</i>
<i>Corinthian leather.</i>

05:52.477 --> 05:55.854
<i>It's perfect for watching that big game</i>
<i>or snoozing to the late show.</i>

05:56.022 --> 05:57.105
