07:09.595 --> 07:12.222
<i>This guy's on a roll, Sylvia.</i>
<i>Think you can catch him?</i>

07:12.598 --> 07:13.974
<i>[ Audience laughs ]</i>

07:13.975 --> 07:14.933
[ Gate opening ]

07:19.147 --> 07:20.522
Now...

07:20.523 --> 07:22.399
...a fuckin' ''B''!

07:22.650 --> 07:26.361
-Baseball, beaver...
-Bastard.

07:27.321 --> 07:29.156
[ Laughing ]

07:29.157 --> 07:30.490
<i>PAUL: How about a ''T'', Steve?</i>

07:30.491 --> 07:31.741
<i>Or barbecue.</i>

07:31.742 --> 07:33.618
[ Continues laughing ]

07:33.619 --> 07:35.203
