07:36.456 --> 07:40.500
...you've been sentenced to die
in the electric chair

07:40.501 --> 07:44.754
for the rape and murder
of 23 men, women, and children.

07:44.755 --> 07:46.465
Do you have any last statement?

07:47.884 --> 07:48.800
24.

07:48.801 --> 07:50.802
[ Moser laughing ]

07:51.220 --> 07:52.971
Fry this sumbitch.

07:54.724 --> 07:57.058
<i>ANNOUNCER:</i>
<i>Ready to hit the jackpot!</i>

07:57.894 --> 07:59.811
<i>[ Audience cheers ]</i>

08:01.230 --> 08:03.148
<i>PAT: I'd like to guess, Steve.</i>

08:03.357 --> 08:05.775
<i>Is it, ''It's just you and me kid''?</i>

08:05.776 --> 08:06.735
- [ Buzzer ]
<i>-AUDIENCE: Aww!</i>

08:07.737 --> 08:09.571
<i>STEVE: Are you ready to take a shot</i>
<i>at that sentence?</i>

08:09.864 --> 08:11.448
[ Audience yelling ]

08:11.741 --> 08:13.074
<i>PAUL: Okay, Steve. Is it...</i>

08:13.284 --> 08:15.285
<i>...''It's just you and me now''?</i>

08:15.912 --> 08:18.205
[ Generator whirring on ]

08:18.539 --> 08:20.290
[ Paul laughing ]

08:20.291 --> 08:22.125
<i>PAUL: Okay! Aw, man.</i>

08:23.503 --> 08:25.212
<i>Congratulations, Paul!</i>

08:25.213 --> 08:26.963
<i>STEVE: ...hit the jackpot.</i>

08:28.382 --> 08:29.591
