08:30.343 --> 08:31.301
Okay.

08:31.969 --> 08:33.178
[ Electrical hum ]

08:35.389 --> 08:36.806
<i>STEVE: Okay. Come on.</i>

08:37.390 --> 08:38.183
<i>Come on.</i>

08:38.518 --> 08:39.601
[ Electrical buzzing ]

08:39.894 --> 08:40.894
<i>PAUL: Yeah!</i>

08:41.062 --> 08:42.020
[ Laughing ]

08:42.188 --> 08:43.230
<i>STEVE: Ladies and gentlemen...</i>

08:47.193 --> 08:48.568
<i>PAUL: Whoo! Whoo! Yeah!</i>

08:50.738 --> 08:53.490
[ Electrical buzzing intensifies ]

08:55.576 --> 08:57.285
<i>STEVE: A trip to paradise!</i>

08:58.746 --> 09:00.372
[ Laughing ]

09:09.632 --> 09:11.341
[ Alarm sounding ]

09:12.677 --> 09:13.843
[ Alarm continues ]

09:13.844 --> 09:15.845
<i>MAN ON PA: All civilians,</i>
<i>please, leave at once!</i>

09:15.846 --> 09:18.390
<i>The prison is now</i>
<i>in a lockdown condition.</i>

09:18.391 --> 09:21.184
<i>All civilians, please,</i>
<i>leave the prison at once!</i>

09:22.228 --> 09:24.980
[ People murmuring ]

09:39.704 --> 09:41.788
''Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.
The sins of...''

09:42.123 --> 09:43.915
[ Choking ]

09:44.834 --> 09:45.750
[ Snapping ]

10:03.394 --> 10:04.436
Agh...

10:05.021 --> 10:07.022
Ain't a pretty picture, is it, bitch?

10:11.235 --> 10:13.570
[ Birds chirping ]

10:15.364 --> 10:16.531
WOMAN: David?

10:16.782 --> 10:17.616
What?

10:23.497 --> 10:24.497
David!

10:27.460 --> 10:28.543
What, Susan?

10:29.420 --> 10:30.295
What?!

10:30.838 --> 10:31.963
This! These!

10:31.964 --> 10:34.049
I mean, it's bad enough
working at the damn prison

10:34.050 --> 10:36.259
without you having to dig up
all this stuff!

10:38.054 --> 10:39.763
Are you having another one
of your nightmares?

10:42.141 --> 10:44.851
They're not my nightmares.
They're your nightmares.

10:48.147 --> 10:50.523
You're having... my nightmare?

10:50.524 --> 10:52.317
Don't poke fun!

10:57.156 --> 10:58.156
Come here.

10:59.825 --> 11:00.992
I'm sorry.

11:08.876 --> 11:10.126
All right.

11:10.711 --> 11:11.878
Now.

11:13.964 --> 11:17.425
It's just... It's just research
for the execution scene

11:17.426 --> 11:19.719
that I have got to write.

11:20.179 --> 11:21.513
Okay?

11:21.806 --> 11:25.350
It's a dream.
It's a bad dream, and it'll go away.

11:34.193 --> 11:37.278
I bet I know what you've been
dreaming about.

11:39.740 --> 11:43.827
I think we'd better do a little
investigative reporting right now.

11:45.413 --> 11:46.746
- [ Alarm ringing ]
<i>-RADIO DJ: But before we get to that,</i>

11:46.747 --> 11:48.206
<i>let's check the traffic for ya.</i>

11:48.207 --> 11:49.249
Oh, shoot!

11:51.752 --> 11:54.212
Why don't you write something funny?

11:54.755 --> 11:56.297
Write a love story.

11:57.258 --> 11:58.883
It's the '80s, Susan.

11:58.884 --> 12:00.760
Love isn't funny!

12:01.721 --> 12:03.555
[ Screaming ]

12:05.015 --> 12:06.933
[ Continues screaming ]

12:12.815 --> 12:15.358
Jesus Christ!
Will you get off my ass?

