12:30.332 --> 12:31.916
Yesterday, it was too loose.

12:32.084 --> 12:35.170
All right, once more, please!
First positions!

12:35.838 --> 12:37.255
Rewire?

12:37.423 --> 12:38.590
Huh?

12:39.592 --> 12:40.967
Are you ready?

12:40.968 --> 12:41.676
Umm...

12:43.387 --> 12:44.304
Yeah.

12:45.639 --> 12:47.557
Okay, let's do it!

