<i>Locally, the glamour and intrigue</i>
<i>surrounding the arrival</i>

12:57.359 --> 13:00.653
<i>of a movie production company</i>
<i>has given way to rumor and suspicion.</i>

13:00.654 --> 13:01.654
WAITRESS: A couple of --

13:01.655 --> 13:03.406
<i>Hollywood's Greystone Productions is</i>
<i>now filming</i>

13:03.407 --> 13:04.407
<i>in the abandoned state penitentiary.</i>

13:04.408 --> 13:05.325
WAITRESS: Two sailors
on a raft, Fingers.

13:05.326 --> 13:07.994
<i>NEWSCASTER: ...which was</i>
<i>destroyed in the riot 18 months ago.</i>

13:08.162 --> 13:09.162
More coffee, sir?

13:09.163 --> 13:10.079
<i>NEWSCASTER: However,</i>
<i>the film's screenwriter,</i>

13:10.080 --> 13:13.166
<i>David Harris, claims his research</i>
<i>for the movie's script</i>

13:13.167 --> 13:15.877
<i>has uncovered the real reasons</i>
<i>for the inmate revolt.</i>

13:16.337 --> 13:18.463
<i>What caused the riot here was...</i>

13:18.672 --> 13:19.756
<i>...brutality...</i>

13:20.382 --> 13:21.800
<i>...inhuman conditions...</i>

13:22.343 --> 13:23.134
<i>...corruption.</i>

13:23.761 --> 13:27.096
<i>DAVID: What went on at this prison</i>
<i>was abominable.</i>

13:27.807 --> 13:31.476
<i>And I think the major ring leader</i>
<i>of that is... is Warden Karsh.</i>

13:31.477 --> 13:34.646
<i>And he's someone that's going to</i>
<i>have to pay for what happened here.</i>

13:34.897 --> 13:36.940
<i>NEWSCASTER: The riot was</i>
<i>the worst in the nation's history,</i>

13:36.941 --> 13:40.151
<i>resulting in the deaths</i>
<i>of 13 guards and 37 inmates.</i>

13:40.152 --> 13:44.280
<i>It began following the execution</i>
<i>of serial killer, Ivan Moser.</i>

13:44.281 --> 13:46.866
<i>Moser was convicted</i>
<i>of the torture-slaying of 23 people,</i>

13:46.867 --> 13:49.619
<i>including game show hostess</i>
<i>Susan Starr.</i>

