They gave her the death penalty.

15:45.194 --> 15:46.736
So, what about Terry?

15:46.904 --> 15:48.613
Was she innocent?

15:48.614 --> 15:49.822
Umm, not exactly.

15:49.823 --> 15:52.575
Turned out,
she was the other woman.

15:53.661 --> 15:55.203
Get out of here!

15:55.204 --> 15:57.372
Kiss your dummy.
There's your other woman.

15:57.581 --> 15:58.373
Uh-huh.

16:02.211 --> 16:04.671
What's the matter, Malone?
You lost your sense of humor?

16:04.922 --> 16:07.799
