I'm serving with you.

16:14.682 --> 16:15.974
[ Malone chuckles ]

16:18.769 --> 16:20.937
2ND ASSISTANT CAMERA:
Scene 96. Take 5.

16:24.817 --> 16:26.401
Action!

16:26.694 --> 16:28.069
[ Gasping ]

16:30.656 --> 16:31.614
[ Guns click ]

16:35.077 --> 16:35.994
