You know, OI' Fingers
is a bit of a celebrity himself.

55:54.726 --> 55:55.934
And why's that?

55:56.102 --> 55:58.896
Mm-hmm. He threw the switch
that fried Ivan Moser

55:58.897 --> 56:01.190
and started the whole damn riot.

56:02.067 --> 56:03.150
You know, these people been

56:03.318 --> 56:05.361
in the old prison goin' on
three weeks, Fingers.

56:05.695 --> 56:07.780
